# Planet Adder config — copy this file to config.txt, edit, then load your save.
# One planet per line: TypeName,row,slot
#   TypeName — one of: Satellite, MetallicAsteroid, RockyAsteroid, CarbonaceousAsteroid,
#              IcyDwarf, OrganicDwarf, DustyDwarf, TerraPlanet, VolcanoPlanet, GasGiant,
#              IceGiant, SaltDwarf, RustPlanet, ForestPlanet, RedDwarf, GoldAsteroid,
#              HydrogenGiant, OilyAsteroid, ShinyPlanet, ChlorinePlanet, SaltDesertPlanet,
#              Wormhole, Earth
#   row      — starmap distance row, 0-based (rockets need range (row+1) x 10,000 km;
#              vanilla rows run 0-16)
#   slot     — orbit position within the row, 0-9
# Lines starting with # are ignored. After the planets are added, this file is renamed
# config.txt.old so they are only ever added once per config.
#
# Example: a Gold Asteroid at 130,000 km and a Terra Planet at 90,000 km:
# GoldAsteroid,12,3
# TerraPlanet,8,6
